---
title: Cal Smart Spiced Chicken Breasts and Lentils with Baby Green Salad
description: Think lentils are boring? Think again! These lentils pack a big flavour punch with zesty Dijon, red wine vinegar and garlic – a perfect companion for juicy, harissa-spiced chicken.

